%% ModelMesh Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.2/modelmesh.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant API as ModelMesh API<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    participant Core as ModelMesh Core<br/>LRU Cache Engine
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS, Cert-based
    participant Remote as Remote ModelMesh Pod<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS, mTLS
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>gRPC plaintext
    participant Storage as Storage Backend

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (Cache Hit)
    Client->>API: gRPC inference request<br/>mm-model-id header<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>Core: Route by model ID
    Core->>Core: LRU cache lookup
    Core->>Runtime: Forward inference (local)<br/>gRPC plaintext :8085/UDS
    Runtime-->>Core: Prediction result
    Core-->>API: Response
    API-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>TLS

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 1b: Model Inference Request (Cache Miss)
    Client->>API: gRPC inference request<br/>mm-model-id header
    API->>Core: Route by model ID
    Core->>Core: LRU cache miss
    Core->>etcd: Lookup model registry<br/>gRPC :2379, TLS
    etcd-->>Core: Model location info
    alt Model on remote pod
        Core->>Remote: Forward request<br/>gRPC Litelinks :8080, TLS/mTLS
        Remote->>Runtime: Local inference<br/>gRPC plaintext
        Runtime-->>Remote: Result
        Remote-->>Core: Response
    else Load model locally
        Core->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC plaintext :8085/UDS
        Runtime->>Storage: Fetch model artifacts
        Storage-->>Runtime: Model data
        Runtime-->>Core: LoadModelResponse (size)
        Core->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC plaintext
        Runtime-->>Core: Prediction result
    end
    Core-->>API: Response
    API-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>TLS

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 2: Model Registration
    Client->>API: registerModel RPC<br/>gRPC :8033, TLS
    API->>Core: Register model
    Core->>etcd: Store model record<br/>gRPC :2379, TLS
    etcd-->>Core: Confirmation
    Core->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC plaintext :8085/UDS
    Runtime->>Storage: Fetch model artifacts
    Storage-->>Runtime: Model data
    Runtime-->>Core: LoadModelResponse
    Core-->>API: ModelStatusInfo
    API-->>Client: Registration response<br/>TLS
